{"tid":193870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行卡綁定支付寶買裝備　10歲男童13天敗光全家財產！","createTime":"2017-04-09T14:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T01:18:59.000Z","uid":35519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01ca54104b860aafeeeef801b9ded92d7d293367","tid":193870,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>銀行卡綁定支付寶買裝備　<br />\n10歲男童13天敗光全家財產！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2157/d2157343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2157%2Fd2157343.jpg&h=d8e1d42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>河北省石家莊1名10歲的藍姓男童玩手機遊戲，竟然偷偷利用爸爸的銀行卡綁定支付寶，短短13天內花光家中所有積蓄。</ins></strong>男童父親近日購買新手機，才赫然發現家中的所有積蓄全都沒了，調閱紀錄才發現，兒子將錢全都用來支付手機遊戲裝備，讓人傻眼不已。<br />\n<br />\n據《河北經視》報導，男童父親表示，近日購買一部新手機，本來打算用支付寶綁定銀行卡，但工作人員表示這張卡已被其他帳號綁定，讓男童父親當場感到不妙，因為他和太太從來不用這些功能。<br />\n<br />\n後來到銀行調查才發現，家中6萬3千元存款（相當台幣31萬元）竟然全都不見了，這一大筆錢被多次轉至「月亮島腐竹」帳戶，轉帳者竟然是夫妻倆的10歲愛子豪豪。<br />\n<br />\n愛玩手機遊戲的豪豪表示，自己日前加入一個群組，群主月亮島腐竹得知豪豪未成年，竟教唆他將父母的銀行卡綁定手機，再要求他以手機支付裝備費用，年幼無知的豪豪在短短13天內，被騙光父母的所有財產。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，月亮島腐竹為了不讓事跡曝光，還要求豪豪每次支付後，將父母手機內的回報簡訊刪除，因此父母從未發現銀行卡的異樣，直到這次購買手機一事，整件事件才因此曝了光。目前石家莊靈壽公安局已立案調查，盼月亮島腐竹能受到法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n網友也留言表示，「10歲了還沒有錢的概念嗎？」、「雙方或多或少都存在問題，不站隊，但我活了20多年都不知道父母的銀行卡密碼」、「這是赤裸裸的詐騙&hellip;」、「這種遊戲管制不嚴，家長對小孩也沒管好」、「可以要回來這些錢，畢竟十歲還是限制行為能力人」。"},{"pid":"f9f40dbc1e672898838e47cbd6590991c0c9e7fc","tid":193870,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d696893bcd5bfaa74e41f056554ef1fa36d2f89","tid":193870,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....."},{"pid":"1abd1076551774e65f0a55ede2e153614feb5ccd","tid":193870,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"唔怕神一般既對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47ac82cf5b1c688f209d54062d3de1fb1cdab6c","tid":193870,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b1744b546bc7945c7ece9470274159e99d1d084","tid":193870,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52465ce746918d10c983691cf8796d04138be66c","tid":193870,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"寧生敗家仔 莫生蠢鈍兒"},{"pid":"c968bc6df9e4b35699b619e55fd27de6affca632","tid":193870,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147581e46ed0c7a0a203cd05e25c3ce94b528011","tid":193870,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔怪得0700做到亞洲股王啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73104d6fbb5885f1a7e48482ab62b11208a8d162","tid":193870,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十幾日用曬6萬幾人仔<br />\n但我比較想知個群主自己食曬d錢定真係幫個靚仔課金<br />\n如果無自己袋落袋，點會算係騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2421cbe484cb987bc6939bb0b2e41586cc9c53d9","tid":193870,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48e8a67033c1973ebbd1a239dc89c4f95fbbcfb","tid":193870,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"終於明點解騰訊升咁撚多<br />\n個個細路都咁做，微軟，google算什麼"},{"pid":"8a7432110e8e219b07d5651fc65277a646cd3a0e","tid":193870,"uid":103983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfa0f3fcd41a8beb4b1bf49be67a1f8384b1112","tid":193870,"uid":42404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T01:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}